name: anon
description: One of the greatest internet lore figures of the 4chan era is anon. It needs no introduction. It was the "No Picture Available" pfp figure that spread across the internet during its time. Anon represents a community cult which is growing day by day. Everyone online is anon. Everyone is welcome as anon. With our website, we make it easy to come onboard and generate memes in throwback 4chan era MS paint style artworks, consistent with anon and internet lore.
